1.00	Artukovic	Andrija Artuković	Andrija Artuković (29 November 1899 – 16 January 1988) was a Croatian politician and lawyer, member of the Ustaše movement and minister in the Government of the Independent State of Croatia. Artuković was convicted of war crimes committed against minorities in the Independent State of Croatia (NDH) during World War II.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/Prisega_vlade_NDH_%282%29.jpg/220px-Prisega_vlade_NDH_%282%29.jpg
